text: TSMC is a major Taiwanese semiconductor manufacturer that is used by Apple to manufacture its bionic chips and recently its M1 series of chips. It also is used by Qualcomm, Huawei, Intel, Google Mediatek, AMD, and Nvidia for their series of chips. == Other websites == * Official website Category:1980s establishments in Taiwan Category:1987 establishments in Asia Category:Electronics companies Category:Companies of Taiwan
